<div class="d-panels font-secondary-light">
<div id="aip_a" class="d-panel p" style="display: none">
<div class="p" id="noi240016aff1">
<sup>1</sup>Department of Biomedical Informatics, Vagelos College of Physicians and Surgeons, Columbia University, New York, New York</div>
<div id="noi240016aff2">
<sup>2</sup>Department of Neurological Surgery, Vagelos College of Physicians and Surgeons, Columbia University, New York, New York</div>
